data.description: Immaculate like new custom floor plan with everything you need in Katima Estates! Meticulously maintained 4bdrm, 3bath, 3car garage(Single car garage side insulated with AC). Spacious living room with modern electric fireplace & dining area combo with new LVP flooring throughout and new paint. Kitchen with granite counter tops, SS appliances with exotic island granite with custom storage and mini fridge. Upstairs game room with mini fridge to keep loaded for entertaining guest.  State of the art 8ch security system covering entire property.  5.1 surround sound system in living room, patio, master bed & bath, game room & garage.  New Rheem water heater.  Whole home water softener. Sprinkler System covers front yard. Large covered patio for outdoor cooking, entertaining and watching the sun set!!
